    "name": "Young Sea Dragon",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Infused with the power of waves and storms, sea dragons\u2014or jiaolungs, as they are known in many lands\u2014are draconic protectors of oceans and their creatures. Possessing tempestuous natures, sea dragons wander widely, sometimes claiming thousands of miles of ocean and coastlines as their protectorates."
        }
    ],
